    "updated_at": "2015-09-10T02:18:30Z",
    "body": "I'm not sure whether it is a bug of your HTML or Chrome engine, but I suggest dumping your page into an independent HTML page and testing it in different browsers, and then report it to Chromium's issues tracker. Electron renders the page exactly the same with Chrome browser, so even if it is a bug of Chrome browser we are not able to fix it on our side.\n"
